<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Winners of essay contest on "Oct. 12, 1492: the Meeting of Two Worlds" were 
announced by USC's Office of Civic and Community Relations. The top four 
winning entrants were Jeffrey Starnes of Riverside, Melody Roof of San Diego, 
Celia Patricia Juarez of El Centro and Araceli Lerma of Garfield High School in 
East Los Angeles. An awards ceremony was held at Plaza de La Raza. 
</P>
