<P>
FUR COATS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Everyone has a right to wear a fur coat. However, before purchasing that fur, 
everyone has an obligation to be fully informed of how a fur coat is made. I 
can assure you that after viewing, personally or by videotape (with sound 
intact), how one captures, raises and skins an animal, one would think twice 
about wearing a fur coat. After all, we are suppose to be intelligent beings. 
</P>
<P>
Let's keep the fur where it belongs-on the animals. 
</P>
<P>
KADY LANE 
</P>
<P>
Pacific Palisades 
