<TEXT>
<P>
Rancho Park Golf Course, which has limited golfers to nine and 12 holes for 
nearly a year because of construction projects, has reopened for a full 18. 
</P>
<P>
Work included installation of a computerized irrigation system, a County Flood 
Control District line that goes through six holes and an oil company pipeline 
through the nine-hole layout. 
</P>
</TEXT>
