Francisco Consort, is the last lecture. 
</P>
<P>
The 7 p.m. lectures will be on Tuesdays Jan. 9, 16, 23 and 30 at Rosemead 
Library, 8800 Valley Blvd.; Wednesdays Jan. 10, 17, 24 and 31 at La Verne 
Library, 3640 D St., and Thursdays Jan. 11, 18 and 25 and Feb. 1 at Hacienda 
Heights Library, 16010 La Monde St. 
</P>
