of Puyo, Ecuador. ; Photo, Children congregate at a crude sawmill in an area of 
Andean cloud forest that is rapidly losing its trees. JAMES F. SMITH / Los 
Angeles Times; Map, Amazon, DON CLEMENT / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
