Chrysler Debt Rating Downgraded: Moody's Investors Service Inc. dropped its 
debt ratings for Chrysler Corp. and its financial subsidiary by one notch amid 
concern over vehicle sales, competition and capital expenditures. Moody's 
rating for Chrysler's senior debt was lowered to BAA2 from BAA1. 
</P>
