<TEXT>
<P>
A former bodyguard for rap singer LL Cool J was convicted of raping a 
15-year-old girl after a concert in the Twin Cities in August. 
</P>
<P>
The Hennepin County District Court jury deliberated about 10 hours before 
issuing a verdict Wednesday night convicting Christopher Tsipouras, 22, Union, 
N.J., of first- and third-degree sexual assault. Judge Philip Bush set 
